<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA34">
<l>pālāḻi nīkiṭakkum paṇpaiyām kēṭṭēyuṅ</l>
<l>kālāḻu neñcaḻiyuṅ kaṇcuḻalu nīlāḻic</l>
<l>cōtiyā yātiyāy tolviṉaiyem pālkaṭiyum</l>
<l>nītiyāy niṟcārntu niṉṟu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As soon as we heard of your nature of lying on the milk ocean</l>
<l>[our] feet faltered, [our] heart softened, [our] eyes span, oh you with the light</l>
<l>of the blue ocean, you beginning, you of right conduct who chases the old deeds</l>
<l>away from us, standing close to you.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
